short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome extension for Spiritual Internet Radio Stations by Saish Patil and Nihar

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Jignasu Chrome Extension plays Spiritual Internet Radio Stations from Prasanthi Nilayam, Isha Sadguru, Golden Temple Amritsar and others. The Radio Extension is for lovers of Sanatana Dharma where Spiritual talks, Music, Vedic Chants and other stations that broadcast such content are made available. The App is built by IT Enthusiasts Saish & Nihar.
